            </div>
            <div class="container">
              <div class="company__body">
                <h2 class="company__title">The company's</h2>
                <div class="company__text">
                  <p>
                    ...Chingford head office boasts a 4000sq ft showroom,
                    featuring over 20 unique full-size displays, and its
                    30,000sq ft factory in Essex is equipped with
                    state-of-the-art machinery, digitally integrated to its
                    offices and cutting edge design and manufacturing systems,
                    to create a fully streamlined business.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Today, Urban Myth employs over 80 people and makes every
                    effort to remain ahead of the curve in the design and
                    manufacture of high-specification kitchens. Kevin and Chris
                    continually invest in the very best talent and technology in
                    order to maintain this position and provide an unrivalled
                    customer experience.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    In summary, Urban Myth challenges convention, whether it’s
                    traditional or contemporary, and believe great design is
                    achievable on any budget.
                  </p>
                </div>
